{"tid":2497143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「金正恩」煽惑包圍新屋嶺加刑囚13個月 上訴庭頒判詞：誣衊警方性侵殺人罪責極嚴重","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T13:12:59.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f72b7694e74d30addd7c703b7331af95490a520c","tid":2497143,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"網名「金正恩」的地盤工前年9月在facebook發文，內含「黑警」、「全民包圍新屋嶺」及「救出義士」等字句，經審訊後被裁定煽惑他人參與非法集結罪成，原判社會服務令160小時，遭律政司覆核刑期。上訴庭早前改判地盤工入獄13個月，今頒下判詞解釋，指被告誣衊警方以極端和殘忍的手法性侵女示威者，甚至活生生打死男示威者，<span class=\"red\">引起憎恨及仇視警方情緒，挑戰警方執法，罪責極嚴重，必須判即時監禁的阻嚇性刑罰</span>。<br />\n<br />\n高院首席法官<span class=\"red\">潘兆初</span>、上訴庭法官<span class=\"red\">彭偉昌</span>及法官<span class=\"red\">潘敏琦</span>上月改判被告入獄13個月，法官潘兆初今頒判詞解釋改判理由。判詞強調，涉及暴力的非法集結罪是嚴重的罪行，判刑必須充分考慮阻嚇和懲罰；同樣地，煽惑他人干犯涉及暴力的非法集結罪也是嚴重罪行，判刑必須具備阻嚇和懲罰。"},{"pid":"f18efbe458f62f315b9568ada761e2516650a530","tid":2497143,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/GPPSLRG3C5HP5FSSVPDUTICFSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FGPPSLRG3C5HP5FSSVPDUTICFSE%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ2t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=bc811642\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FGPPSLRG3C5HP5FSSVPDUTICFSE%2F&h=ac574153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/GPPSLRG3C5HP5FSSVPDUTICFSE/</a>"},{"pid":"d7019b9bff90b2436c31d356c9bd81af24e8ca76","tid":2497143,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4edca3480330a078a381e6391361b00fae7729","tid":2497143,"uid":271395,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"誣衊示威者彈珠射爆眼呢？仲要